{"tid":1640439,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"摩根: 避免投資香港銀行股 (依家明777點解試行緊急法)","createTime":"2019-10-09T03:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T03:42:04.000Z","uid":305299,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50a8ca8939ae90e68c86fec4338a226d634ee3d8","tid":1640439,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hxfmbjK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhxfmbjK.jpg&h=3e4a9935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家睇睇份新聞內容，摩根士丹利係無提抗爭行為，而係大環境原因令佢地得出個咁嘅結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家認真要逐步搬啲錢離開香港銀行系統，走唔到嘅都要考慮開個美帝花旗戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />777依家動用緊急法，好可能就係為咗之後管制大家啲血汗錢去救中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n=====新聞報導=====<br />\n<strong>港銀全線受壓 大摩降行業評級 叫沽滙控 恒生</strong><br />\n【信報財經新聞】本地銀行股全線低開，滙控(00005)甫開挫1.5%，報57.6元創逾一個月低，現跌1.4%；恒生(00011)曾挫3%，最新挫2.5%；渣打(02888)低開1.3%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中銀香港(02388)跌1.2%；東亞(00023)續創十年低，最新挫1.7%。<br />\n<br />\n摩根士丹利發表報告，把香港銀行業的評級下調至「謹慎」，當中滙控和恒生評級降至「減持」。<br />\n<br />\n大摩指，由於本地經濟放緩、低利率和更多的市場競爭，下調港銀今年及未來兩年盈利預測，當中2020/2021年的盈利預測，較市場預期平均低約15%至20%。<br />\n<br />\n該行認為，虛擬銀行將會加劇零售業務競爭，恒生、滙控和渣打將面臨更大壓力，因三家銀行約50%的香港收入來自零售業務。<br />\n<br />\n大摩表示，滙控股息率可為股價提供支持，不過無論在香港抑或歐洲市場，其估值都顯得昂貴。<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=539054&amp;type=analysis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fnews%2Fpost.php%3Fid%3D539054%26type%3Danalysis&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=c50cb82a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=539054&amp;type=analysis</a>"},{"pid":"3ae6ad47f07e9c0758c735fceb1b21faa79def7c","tid":1640439,"uid":59608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:24:55.000Z","msg":"繼續坐貨損手爛腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝其他港豬比我地有機會走"},{"pid":"a5be4a85ab326982e8ca917b8d0db80fccf2a938","tid":1640439,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70193a2f6b43e73771fb7d9ffdbd14a046b5467","tid":1640439,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"11跌3.45%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33955102df4567b098feb9d6a3aea83d5bc1cf6","tid":1640439,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"大型和平遊行呀!<br />\n唔帶gear, 淨係戴口罩!<br />\n終點集會!<br />\n完咗屋企張床要人!<br />\n有冇好日? 最好係公眾假期!"}]}